11
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:54,700
<i>O viaţă plină de umilinţă.</i>

12
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:56,000
<i>Şi respingere.</i>

13
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,600
Da!

14
00:01:22,900 --> 00:01:24,300
